Language: en

00:00:04.839 --> 00:00:09.219
JetPens presents 
the Neo Critz pencil case from Kokuyo of Japan.

00:00:10.260 --> 00:00:13.680
The New Critz is Kokuyo's best selling pencil case line.

00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:17.120
It was one of the first pencil cases
with an "upright standing" design

00:00:17.120 --> 00:00:19.660
that functions as a pen holder when "folded down".

00:00:20.440 --> 00:00:21.680
 As a standing pen holder,

00:00:21.690 --> 00:00:27.050
the case takes little space on the desk and
makes it easy to pick out the item you need.

00:00:37.660 --> 00:00:41.160
 The Neo Critz is the perfect
organization tool for everyone.

00:00:58.960 --> 00:01:01.560
The case, measuring 19 cm in height,

00:01:01.560 --> 00:01:06.380
has a generous main compartment
that holds items both long and wide. 

00:01:06.520 --> 00:01:10.360
The front pocket allows
for easy accessibility of small stationery items

00:01:10.720 --> 00:01:12.020
like an eraser. 

00:01:12.020 --> 00:01:17.760
In addition, there is a slot on one side of the case with a velcro enclosure for additional organization.

00:01:18.340 --> 00:01:23.320
The pencil case is made of high quality nylon that's extremely durable and abrasion-resistant.

00:01:23.320 --> 00:01:27.800
The outside fabric design differs from the inside,
with the zipper color matching the interior. 

00:01:28.080 --> 00:01:32.260
The entire shell of the pencil case is cushioned, protecting the items stored inside. 

00:01:32.560 --> 00:01:36.320
The bottom half of the pencil case
is further reinforced with polypropylene,

00:01:36.320 --> 00:01:39.240
allowing it to hold its shape while acting as a pen holder. 

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:44.400
A special feature of this tried and true pencil case
is the double-zipper.

00:01:44.419 --> 00:01:47.939
The case can be closed or opened
by the zipper on either side.

00:01:52.480 --> 00:01:57.140
Moreover, when stored upright in your bag, 
the case can be unzipped from the top only, 

00:01:57.140 --> 00:02:00.840
making it easy for you to grab your pens
without having to take the case out.

00:02:01.660 --> 00:02:06.080
The Neo Critz is also available in a mini size with more fun color combinations. 

00:02:10.860 --> 00:02:13.700
Pen case and pen stand.
Two in one.

